ica page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.45633, "shard": "04", "shelf_id": "sn83045012, 1930-08-15, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/ohi", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["newspapers", "butler", "hamilton (ohio)", "hamilton", "ohio", "united states"], "subject_headings": ["Hamilton (Ohio)--Newspapers", "Ohio--Hamilton", "United States--Ohio--Butler--Hamilton"], "subjects": [{"butler": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:butler&fo=json"}, {"hamilton": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hamilton&fo=json"}, {"hamilton (ohio)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hamilton+%28ohio%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"ohio": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:ohio&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2023-09-05T03:39:23.874Z", "title": "The Butler County press (Hamilton, Ohio), August 15, 1930", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn83045012/1930-08-15/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn83045012/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn83045012", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/fd7ac55e-b367-58b7-8194-1cf7ba85e0e2"], "batch": ["ohi_buttercup_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1900", "description": ["Weekly Began Apr. 22, 1900. Cf. NIM, 1973-1977. -v. 46, no. 21 (Aug. 30, 1946). Archived issues are available in digital format from t